name: House M.D. - Episode 3: Skull and Bones
name_original: House M.D. - Episode 3: Skull and Bones
description:
A macho college kid loses feeling in his arms during a fraternaty hazing. Track down the correct diagnosis by interviewing and examining the patient, running lab tests, and even performing surgery. Every piece of evidence reveals part of the solution, so careful observation and analysis is key. The clock is ticking, but be prepared for multiple twists and turns before you solve the case.

Features

• Join Dr. House and his elite diagnostic team.
• Race against the clock to solve a new medical mystery.
